    <item>
      <title>爱荷华州驱逐法因越权而受到美国起诉的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/iowa-deportation-law-draws-threat-to-sue-from-us-as-overreach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府告诉爱荷华州，它将提起诉讼，阻止一项新法律，该法律将被驱逐出境后重新进入该州视为犯罪，称该法律受到联邦法律的先发制人，破坏了对外关系，并实际上创建了第二个移民制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/iowa-deportation-law-draws-threat-to-sue-from-us-as-overreach</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 22:18:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
